          <span class="reviews-count">4.8 out of 5 &middot; 164 Google reviews</span>
        </div>
        <div class="reviews-grid">

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <blockquote>"Greenleaf have been maintaining our garden for three years now. Reliable, tidy and the lawn has never looked better. They turn up when they say they will and always leave the place spotless."</blockquote>
            <div class="reviewer">
              <div class="reviewer-avatar">JT</div>
              <div>
                <strong>James T.</strong>
                <span>Sidmouth</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <blockquote>"Hired them for a full garden clearance after we moved in. They transformed a complete jungle into something beautiful in a single day. Brilliant team, great price. Could not recommend more."</blockquote>
            <div class="reviewer">
              <div class="reviewer-avatar">CW</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Carol W.</strong>
                <span>Budleigh Salterton</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="review-card">
            <div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div>
            <blockquote>"Excellent work on our hedges and borders. Very professional team who clearly know their stuff. Fair pricing, no hidden extras. Already booked them in for the autumn tidy-up."</blockquote>
            <div class="reviewer">
              <div class="reviewer-avatar">MD</div>
              <div>
                <strong>Mark D.</strong>
                <span>Ottery St Mary</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. WHY US / ABOUT -->
    <section id="about" class="about">
      <div class="container about-inner">
        <div class="about-content">
          <p class="section-eyebrow">Why Choose Greenleaf</p>
          <h2>19 Years Growing <em>East Devon Gardens</em></h2>
          <p>Founded in Sidmouth in 2007, Greenleaf Garden Services has become one of the most trusted names in East Devon horticulture. Our team of trained gardeners and arborists brings a genuine passion for the outdoors to every job, whether that is a weekly lawn visit or a complete garden redesign.</p>
          <p>We work with homeowners, landlords and holiday lets across the region, building long-term relationships built on consistent, high-quality work. Every member of our team is DBS checked, fully insured, and committed to leaving your property better than we found it.</p>
          <ul class="about-list">
            <li>
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              RHS-trained horticulturalists on every team
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              NPTC qualified for tree and chainsaw work
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              10 million public liability cover
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              Checkatrade verified with 300+ reviews
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">1,400+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Gardens maintained</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">19</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years of experience</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">8</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Full-time gardeners</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">98%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Would recommend us</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

